author: Minecraft
description: Are you ready to find out what’s inside an elder guardian? Trust us, you aren’t – but we’ll show you anyway! Elder guardians are a source of both Fatigue and nightmares. Why are they so aggressive? What are they really guarding and why do they attack squids? Jens Bergensten, Agnes Larsson, Samuel Åberg, and Laura de Llorens answer these questions as we force them to look an elder guardian in its huge eye.
title: Why are their eyes so big? | The Story Of The Elder Guardian
